data.description: Welcome home to this NO HOA, 1 story, large corner lot! Cozy 3 bedroom/2 bath/2 garage home features kitchen with quartz countertops and lots of storage and large dining area. Laminate wood flooring in living spaces and carpet in bedrooms. Skylight in 2nd bath. Cathedral ceilings in living room. Back yard is all concrete for low maintenance. Call today to schedule appt- this won't last long!
